CONFIGURE

1) Upload the files to any web server
2) Edit the config.inc and insert your Disqus API key and the forum ID for your login
3) Open the extract.php in your web browser and it will print a list of all of your e-mail addresses


__________________________________________________________________


DISQUS API INSTRUCTIONS

You can get your DISQUS API key here (you must already be logged in):
http://disqus.com/api/get_my_key/

Then you can get your DISQUS forum ID from this URL:
http://disqus.com/api/get_forum_list?user_api_key=API_KEY_HERE&api_version=1.1

